{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/0.gif?t=1737535678\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the shoes of Agent Kim, a seasoned private investigator drawn into a chilling mystery deep in the wilderness. Nine people have vanished from an eerie villa over the past 20 years, including your latest client\u2019s adventurous relative, Mr. Lin. The police have failed to uncover any leads, leaving the task of solving this haunting puzzle to you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/1.gif?t=1737535678\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">After sneaking into the villa, you\u2019re struck by an unknown force and awaken in a cold, desolate room. The air is thick with dread as you realize you\u2019ve become the latest prisoner of this cursed mansion. With danger lurking around every corner and the undead stalking your every move, it\u2019s a race against time to escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/8.gif?t=1737535678\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore the villa\u2019s dark corridors, uncover its sinister past, and piece together the terrifying truth behind the disappearances. Find hidden clues, solve intricate puzzles, and outsmart the relentless zombies that roam the estate. Your only hope is to escape before becoming another soul lost to the mansion\u2019s curse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/extras/5.gif?t=1737535678\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Will you make it out alive, or will you too vanish without a trace?</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3304750/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1737